\hline 
Sum, product & sum(), prod()\\
\hline \\
$\pi$  & pi\\
\hline 
Infinity & Inf, -Inf (infinity)\\
\hline 
Not defined & NaN (Not a number)\\
\hline 
Missing values & NA (Not available)\\
\hline 
Empty set & NULL\\
\hline 
